rows.label: tev016501_MSG0001
rows.name:
One day he just came home looking like that.
Even his oldest acquaintances were taken aback.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016501_MSG0002
rows.name:
Mom was totally creeped out at having a husband
who looked younger than her own son.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016501_MSG0003
rows.name:
They broke up as soon as we arrived on Mira.
Now it's just the two of us living together.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016501_MSG0004
rows.name:
Nevertheless, Dad doesn't seem to regret it one bit.
I gotta admit, I kind of admire that about him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016501_MSG0005
rows.name:
Always finish the job, no matter whatâ€”that's
Cole Family Rule Number Two. Pretty straightforward.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016501_MSG0008
rows.name:
The other day, Irina told me that as long as she lived,
she'd never understand the way me and my father
operate.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016501_MSG0009
rows.name:
My father and I may be family, but we're still our
own people. She just doesn't seem to get that way
of thinking, I guess.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016501_MSG0010
rows.name:
That caused me to ask what Irina's family was like,
but as soon as I did, she got strangely quiet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016501_MSG0011
rows.name:
Then she whispered something about how she would
have wanted to save her family even if it cost her own
life.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016501_MSG0012
rows.name:
She seemed pretty upset about it.
Do you think I shouldn't have asked?[ST:wait ]
